These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, trance, ambient
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
3. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | trance | techno |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, february
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Birthday   | january | february | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, eggplant, cherry
1. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
2. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Food   | lettuce | eggplant | cherry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
